<div class="page">
<a name="Title"><h1 class="center">CS112: Homework 5</h1></a>
Start this assignment early! (There is a decent chance that pygame
isn't installed correctly on your personal computer, if you start this
early you'll have a chance to correct this and still get the
assignment in on time)
<p>
This assignment is all about drawing pictures. Create 3 separate
programs that each create an interesting image. As long as the images
you create with pygame and draw are interesting you've done the
assignment. Please feel free to play with more of pygame if you want,
simple drawings are the minimal.
<p>
Turning it in:<br>
<ol>
<li>Create a zipped archive of all the files associated with this
assignment and name it with your name and the homework assignment (for
example paulDicksonHW5.zip).</li> 
<li>Place a copy of this zipped archive in the handin folder for the
  class on urza.</li>
<li>Send an e-mail saying you've turned it in with the following format:<br>
To: pedcs-at-hampshire.edu
<br>Subject: 112-HW5: Your name</li>
</ol>

